description: Lists all the resource associations for the specified Route 53 Profile.

parameters.name: MaxResults
parameters.description: The maximum number of objects that you want to return for this request. If more objects are available, in the response, a NextToken value, which you can use in a subsequent call to get the next batch of objects, is provided. If you don't specify a value for MaxResults, up to 100 objects are returned.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description: For the first call to this list request, omit this value. When you request a list of objects, at most the number of objects specified by MaxResults is returned. If more objects are available for retrieval, a NextToken value is returned in the response. To retrieve the next batch of objects, use the token that was returned for the prior request in your next request.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If more than MaxResults resource associations match the specified criteria, you can submit another ListProfileResourceAssociations request to get the next group of results. In the next request, specify the value of NextToken from the previous response.

nested_items.name: ProfileResourceAssociations
nested_items.description: Information about the profile resource association that you specified in a GetProfileResourceAssociation request.

nested_items.name: CreationTime
nested_items.description: The date and time that the Profile resource association was created, in Unix time format and Coordinated Universal Time (UTC).

nested_items.name: Id
nested_items.description: ID of the Profile resource association.

nested_items.name: ModificationTime
nested_items.description: The date and time that the Profile resource association was modified, in Unix time format and Coordinated Universal Time (UTC).

nested_items.name: Name
nested_items.description: Name of the Profile resource association.

nested_items.name: OwnerId
nested_items.description: Amazon Web Services account ID of the Profile resource association owner.

nested_items.name: ProfileId
nested_items.description: Profile ID of the Profile that the resources are associated with.

nested_items.name: ResourceArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the resource association.

nested_items.name: ResourceProperties
nested_items.description: If the DNS resource is a DNS Firewall rule group, this indicates the priority.

nested_items.name: ResourceType
nested_items.description: Resource type, such as a private hosted zone, or DNS Firewall rule group.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: Status of the Profile resource association.

nested_items.name: StatusMessage
nested_items.description: Additional information about the Profile resource association.
